    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1917-12-17T11:14:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1917-12-17T11:14:00-05:00" n="576"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d576">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 763.72111/6825</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Minister in Ecuador</hi> (<persName corresp="#p_HCS1"
                        type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Hartman</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Quito</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1917-12-17T11:00:00-05:14">
                            <hi rend="italic">December 17, 1917, 11 a.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                        <lb/> [<hi rend="italic">Received 4.05 p.m.</hi>]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Note from the Minister for Foreign Affairs says that Ecuadoran Government will
                    receive in Ecuadoran waters friendly war vessels <pb facs="0563" n="391"
                        xml:id="pg_391"/> without subjecting them to restrictions in force against
                    belligerent war vessels, and that wireless station at Salinas will receive and
                    send telegrams from and to said vessels.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_HCS1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Hartman</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
